item.title: Where do i find the file
item.dc:creator: @tonypker13 tonypker13
item.description:
@tonypker13 wrote:

Ok download the file. Then make a new folder on your desktop. Then, you open up winrar. After that, look for the file name you downloaded. Click it ONCE, then click extract at the top of the screen. A list will come up with places you can extract it to. Look through until you find your file. click it and press Ok.
You have now extracted.
